The following sites are known to mirror
ftp://ftp.tcl.tk/pub/tcl
If you decide to mirror this site, please contact 
webmaster@tcl.tk so we can update our list.
See also the Tcl Developer Xchange at
http://www.tcl.tk (formerly / aka http://dev.scriptics.com/)

